data.description: Come see this CBS 2 bedroom 1 bath Key West home.  Wood floors in main living area and bedrooms, kitchen features center island, upgraded cabinetry, newer top of the line Stainless Steel appliances-Newer hardware and sink-New metal roof in 2014-New drainfield in 2014, New windows in 2002-New pump for well in 2015 and a large fenced backyard area.Key upgrades include a recent AC replacement in 2021, an upgraded 200 AMP meter, and a convenient switch to city water, also completed in 2021. The layout offers versatility with two generously spaced bedrooms that provide privacy from one another. Additionally, there's a flexible living area that could easily be be transformed into a third bedroom, an office/den, or a formal dining room, catering to your specific needs.
